Command:

```cmd
CustomCertificationServer.exe packt.dat
```

What it does:

```text
Starts the custom CertificationServer and loads packt.dat as its certification database/config source.
```

Expected output:

```text
Certification Server started on 127.0.0.1:32000
```

This means:

```text
The CertificationServer is listening on port 32000.
```

